    "description": "<p><strong>Xincheng Group is a business consulting company specializing in immigration, family office, wealth management, overseas company registration, bank account opening, real estate, tax planning, overseas passports and other services. We have many service organizations in Singapore and China.</strong><br>\n<strong>We are committed to providing private customized solutions for high-net-worth families, and provide one-stop services from children's education to company operations to asset allocation to asset inheritance. Through accurate analysis and positioning, we provide a full set of solutions tailored to customers to ensure high efficiency and high success rate.</strong></p>",
